import React, { useState } from 'react'
import {
    Flex, 
    Text, 
    IconButton, 
    Divider, 
    Avatar, 
    Heading
} from '@chakra-ui/react'

 function Navbar() {
    return (
        <Flex 
            position="fixed"
            top = "5px"
            width="100%"
            flexDir="row"
            justifyContent="space-between"
        >
            <Flex
                p="5%"
                flexDir="row"
                w="100%"
                alignItems="flex-start"
                mb={4}
            >
                <Divider/>
                <Flex>
                    <Avatar/>
                    <Flex>
                        <Heading>USER</Heading>
                        <Text>MEMBER</Text>
                    </Flex>
                </Flex>
            
            </Flex>

        </Flex>
    )
}

export default Navbar;
